{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images","result":{"pageContext":{"id":109,"date":"2020-12-05T08:57:55","date_gmt":"2020-12-05T08:57:55","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=109"},"modified":"2021-01-04T03:44:33","modified_gmt":"2021-01-04T03:44:33","slug":"debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images/","title":{"rendered":"Debut Theme: enable swiping to product page images"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Debut theme is, undoubtedly, one of the best themes out there be it paid or free. However it comes with one big flaw complained by many that is its product page lacking a proper swiping functionality to improve the UX of the website. <br><br>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll teach you step-by-step how to implement a swiping functionality for Debut theme. <br><br>There are two options:<br>Download the <strong>free version</strong> clicking <a href=\"https://gumroad.com/l/debut-slider-free\">here</a> (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://debut-theme-slider-free.myshopify.com/products/blue-silk-tuxedo\" target=\"_blank\">live preview</a>) &#8211; <strong>password</strong> is: 123<br>Download the <strong>pro version</strong> clicking <a href=\"https://www.fatfreecartpro.com/ecom/gb.php?&amp;c=cart&amp;ejc=2&amp;cl=374804&amp;i=1689291\">here</a>. (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://debut-theme-slider.myshopify.com/products/blue-silk-tuxedo\" target=\"_blank\">live preview</a>)<br><br>The main differences are:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Features </th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Pro</th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Free</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Swipe featured image</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Swipe thumbnails</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Arrows for thumbnails </td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Loop thumbnail images</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Change image on variant change</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Zoom on hover</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Loop featured image</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Works with multiple dropdown variants</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Arrows for featured image</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Choose how many thumbnails<br>to show</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Change arrows color<br>(for both thumbnail and featured image)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">&#8220;Featured product section&#8221; <br>also working with slider</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> ✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Frequent updates</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Bug fixes</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Constantly maintained </td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">New features based on user feedback</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>More details about the <strong>pro</strong> version can be found <a href=\"https://ezfy.e-junkie.com/product/1689291\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Getting ready and downloading the code files</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Now that you have the Shopify admin ready to go, download the code files for the <a href=\"https://gumroad.com/l/debut-slider-free\">free version</a> (you can put <em>0</em> for the price so you don&#8217;t pay nothing) or the <a href=\"https://gumroad.com/l/debut-slider-pro\">pro </a><a href=\"https://www.fatfreecartpro.com/ecom/gb.php?&amp;c=cart&amp;ejc=2&amp;cl=374804&amp;i=1689291\">version</a>.  Just enter your email, choose payment form (if you chose the pro version) and you&#8217;ll receive a download link.</li><li>In the download there will be two files: <strong>product-template.txt </strong>and <strong>javascript.txt</strong>. The installation process is the exact same for both free and pro.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Setting up the product-template file<br>The first thing we have to do is to prepare the product page.</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open the <strong>product-template.txt </strong>file and copy all the code in there.</li><li>Now go back to your Shopify admin, find the <strong>product-template.liquid</strong> file in your theme.</li><li>Delete everything in there and paste the code that you copied.</li><li>Save. It should look like this:</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"776\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1200x776.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-110\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1200x776.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-600x388.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-768x496.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image.png 1230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure that the very first line is <strong>{% assign enable_thumbnail_slider_desktop = true %} </strong>just like in the image above.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Setting up Javascript files</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Now open the downloaded file named <strong>javascript.txt</strong> and copy all the code in there.</li><li>In your Shopify theme, find the file <strong>theme.js</strong>.</li><li>Scroll all the way down and, at the very bottom of the file, paste the code.</li><li>Click on &#8220;save&#8221;.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"764\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1-1200x764.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-112\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1-1200x764.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1-600x382.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1-768x489.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1.png 1295w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Setting up exclusive PRO version files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the pro version you&#8217;ll receive an extra file called <strong>featured-product.txt</strong>. It allows you to implement the slider with the section Featured Product in Debut. <strong>Please keep in mind that you can use one section with this.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ol id=\"block-f91f6f4c-e07e-4749-bf87-2a50ff0d3845\"><li>Open the downloaded file named <strong>featured-product.txt</strong> and copy all the code in there.</li><li>In your Shopify theme, find the file <strong>featured-product.liquid</strong>.</li><li>Delete everything in there and paste the code that you copied.</li><li>Click on &#8220;save&#8221;.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>That is it! Any questions or concerns? Just reach out to us and we&#8217;ll help you out as soon as possible.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ever wanted to enable &#8220;swiping&#8221; on your Debut theme product images? Now it&#8217;s possible. And it takes less than 2 minutes.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":125,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","forma